 elementor-element-c6d8b07 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"c6d8b07\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>We may collect information about you whenever you interact with us. For example, when you contact regarding our activities, register as a supporter, send or receive information or sign a petition, you specifically and knowingly provide us with your personal information. We may also receive information about you from third parties \u2013 but only if you have given them permission to share your information.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c9dbe67 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"c9dbe67\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Confidentiality<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-39bad26 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"39bad26\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>We will not be responsible for the privacy of data collected by websites not owned or managed by Charity, including those linked through our website.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a7ac7aa elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"a7ac7aa\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Making a complaint\n<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-652265f elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"652265f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>If you are not satisfied with the response, please contact us at eagle-elite@email.com with the details explaining your concerns. We will review your complaint and investigate if the right procedures have been followed and respond back to you as appropriate. We aim to complete this investigation within 15 working days of receiving your complaint, however, in some cases it may take longer. If you are still unsatisfied with the response, you may contact us.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Privacy Policy Information<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":25,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","template":"","meta":{"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-3","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/clanyeco.vamtam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/3","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/clanyeco.vamtam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/clanyeco.vamtam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/clanyeco.vamtam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/clanyeco.vamtam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=3"}],"version-history":[{"count":7,"href":"https:\/\/clanyeco.vamtam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/3\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":7705,"href":"https:\/\/clanyeco.vamtam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/3\/revisions\/7705"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/clanyeco.vamtam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/25"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/clanyeco.vamtam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=3"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","hre